Even if I give 100% to everything, I'll never get what I want. Because I never have. Not even remotely. I've just lost everything. Does it even make sense to do anything anymore?

But honestly I don't have the strength to be confident again or to be myself ever again. Even if I make it through this, it will just happen again. And I just can't. All I want is peace at this point. Wish I could disconnect from everything for sometime.

I am physically and mentally drained at this point and struggling to even find a will to wake up and work every morning. 2 years back I was in the same phase but I bounced back. And people keep telling me it will get better this time too.

Everything went downhill in the past 6 months, and honestly it doesn't seem to stop. It just gets worse with every passing day. Trying to fight everything with all the strength I have, but nothing seems to work. Doesn't even get better.
